x.php?case=archive&act=list&catid=43 Guangzhou R&F F.C.]|language=zh|date=January 2019}}\n\n==== Academy ====\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Position\n!Staff\n|-\n|Academy director||{{flagicon|Japan}} [[Shiro Kikuhara]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"|Academy coach||{{flagicon|Japan}} [[Mitsunori Yabuta]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Japan}} [[Tsuyoshi Yoshitake]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Japan}} [[Yuki Fujimoto]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Japan}} Ryu Hirose\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Japan}} Daichi Suzuki\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Japan}} Hiroshi Yoshida\n|-\n{{Fb oi footer|s=[http://www.gzrffc.com.cn/index.php?case=archive&act=show&aid=6758 Guangzhou R&F F.C.]|language=zh|date=August 2019}}\n\n== Managerial history ==\n{{main|List of Guangzhou R&F F.C. managers}}\n\n{{updated|24 August 2016}}.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldfootball.net/teams/guangzhou-r-f/9/|title=Guangzhou R&F \" Manager history|publisher=worldfootball.net|accessdate=2015-01-09|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110001441/http://www.worldfootball.net/teams/guangzhou-r-f/9/|archivedate=2015-01-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thefinalball.com/equipa.php?id=3922&menu=coaches|title=Guangzhou R&F Football Club|publisher=footballzz.co.uk|accessdate=2015-01-09|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140519163503/http://www.footballzz.co.uk/equipa.php?id=3922|archivedate=2014-05-19}}</ref>\n\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n*{{flagicon|Ukraine}} [[Serhiy Morozov]] (1994)\n*{{flagicon|China}} [[Zhang Zengqun]] (1995)\n*{{flagicon|China}} [[Li Yingfa]] (1996)\n*{{flagicon|China}} [[Li Qiang (football manager)|Li Qiang]] (1996\u201398)\n*{{flagicon|Brazil}} [[Ademar Braga (football manager)|Ademar Braga]] (1999)\n*{{flagicon|China}} [[Li Qiang (football manager)|Li Qiang]] (1999)\n*{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Valery Nepomnyashchy]] (2000)\n*{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Henryk Kasperczak]] (2000\u201301)\n*{{flagicon|France}} [[Alain Laurier]] (2001)\n*{{flagicon|Portugal}} [[Toni (footballer, born 1946)|Toni]] (July 1, 2002&nbsp;\