entown (2014), 6\u20132 v Yanbian Funde (2017)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/guangzhou-rf-vs-yanbian-fude-fc/370118|title=Chinese Super League (Sky Sports)|website=SkySports|language=en|access-date=2018-12-23}}</ref>\n*'''Record away victory''': 5\u20131 v [[Liaoning Whowin F.C.|Liaoning Whowin FC]] (2014)\n* '''Record home defeat''': 2\u20136 v [[Tianjin Tianhai F.C.|Tianjin Quanjian]] (2018)\n* '''Record away defea'''t: 0\u20136 v [[Beijing Sinobo Guoan F.C.|Beijing Guoan]] (2013)\n* '''Most [[Shutout|cleansheets]]''': 9 (2014)\n* '''Fewest cleansheets''': 5 (2012, 2017, 2018)\n\n=== Player records ===\n\n* '''Top domestic goalscorer''': 20, [[Xiao Zhi]]\n* '''Top foreign goalscorer''': 58, [[Eran Zahavi]]\n* '''Youngest domestic goalscorer''': 20 years old (2018) [[Ma Junliang]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://sports.163.com/18/0505/23/DH31UP2700058780.html|title=\u5bcc\u529b20\u5c81\u5c0f\u5c06:\u8fdb\u7403\u56e0\u8fd0\u6c14\u597d \u613f\u4e0d\u9760\u65b0\u653f\u4e5f\u53ef\u8e22\u6bd4\u8d5b|website=Net Ease Sports|access-date=2018-12-16}}</ref>\n* '''Youngest foreign goalscorer''': 19 years old (2014) [[Aaron Samuel Olanare]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://sports.163.com/14/0731/22/A2H0VCDG00051C89.html|title=\u5b9e\u5f55-\u6734\u949f\u4f51\u4e16\u754c\u6ce2\u963f\u9686\u9996\u7403 \u5bcc\u529b\u5ba2\u573a5\u20131\u706d\u8fbd\u8db3|date=2014-07-31|website=Net Ease Sports|access-date=2018-12-16}}</ref>\n* '''Most goals in a season''': 29 (2019) Eran Zahavi<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/israels-zahavi-sets-single-season-scoring-record-in-chinese-soccer/|title=Israel\u2019s Zahavi sets single season scoring record for Chinese soccer|last=staff|first=T. O. I.|website=www.timesofisrael.com|language=en-US|access-date=2020-01-11}}</ref>\n* '''Fastest hat-trick''': 10 minutes (2014) [[Abderrazak Hamdallah|Abderazzak Hamdallah]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://wildeastfootball.net/2014/03/guangzhou-rf-swamp-hangzhou-greentown/|title=Guangzhou R&F Swamp Hangzhou Greentown|last=Ross|first=Donald|date=2014-03-31|website=Wild East Football|language=en-GB|access-date=2018-12-23}}</ref>\n* '''Most appearances by a goalkeeper''': 168, [[Cheng Yuelei]]\n* '''Most appearances by an outfield player''': 200, [[Tang Miao (footballer, born October 1990)|Tang Miao]]\n* '''Oldest player''': 35 years, 6 months, 23 days, [[Zhang Yaokun]]\n\n== Results ==\n=== All-time League rankings ===\n\n''As of the end of 2018 season.''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesc/chinahist.html |title=China League History |publisher=rsssf.com |date=22 Oct 2009 |accessdate=24 January 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607124048/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesc/chinahist.html |archivedate=7 June 2014 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sodasoccer.com/search/club/3/5791/E0069B2C301B9794.shtml|title=\u5e7f\u5dde\u5bcc\u529b|publisher=sodasoccer.com|accessdate=24 January 2014|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140217223426/http://www.sodasoccer.com/search/club/3/5791/E0069B2C301B9794.shtml|archivedate=17 February 2014}}</ref>\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=100% style=text-align:Center\n|-\n!Year\n!Div\n!{{Tooltip|Pld|Matches played}}\n!{{Tooltip|W|Matches won}}\n!{{Tooltip|D|Matches drawn}}\n!{{Tooltip|L|Match(es) lost}}\n!{{Tooltip|GF|Goals for}}\n!{{Tooltip|GA|Goals against}}\n!{{Tooltip|GD|Goal difference}}\n!Pts\n!width=2%|Pos.\n!width=4%|[[Chinese FA Cup|FA Cup]]\n!width=2%|[[Chinese FA Super Cup|Super Cup]]\n!width=2%|[[League Cup]]\n!|[[Asian Football Confederation|AFC]]\n!Att./G\n!Stadium\n|-\n| 1986 || bgcolor=#FFFFE0|2 || 7 || || || || || || || || 4{{ref| 1| 1}} || DNQ ||&nbsp;\u2013 ||&nbsp;\u2013 || || ||  \n|-\n| 1987 || 3 || 7 || || || || || || || || 3{{ref| 1| 1}}{{ref| 2| 2}} || {{grey|NH}} ||&nbsp;\u2013 ||&nbsp;\u2013 || || ||  \n|-\n| [[Chinese Jia-A League 1988|1988]] || bgcolor=#D0F0C0|1 || 20 || 4 || 7 || 9 || 17 || 17 || 0 || 19 || bgcolor=#ffcccc|17 |